{"tid":305424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃中國區附加賽名額決定賽－劉詩詩vs劉亦菲","createTime":"2017-07-01T16:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T16:30:45.000Z","uid":92376,"like":34,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e561772b1682366f695168643153d0adac5a5ccf","tid":305424,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃中國區附加賽名額決定賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-2 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/LoYkbse.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLoYkbse.png&h=fa66d5e0&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JOPuxPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJOPuxPx.png&h=bcbd8b42&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">劉詩詩 vs 劉亦菲</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本帖發起後22小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"11a6e693182147141559b4dd99dda9404c58ce2a","tid":305424,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"解釋一下,呢場比賽係win or nothing<br />\n贏仲可以拎到中國區既附加賽席位,有一線生機晉身分組賽<br />\n輸左就會直接淘汰架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2564bf274e7b32c247424a3ad9a7097c9cd2237","tid":305424,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88d3f4ee124786fdaa70c84a